              <h2>Gardens & Edible Landscapes</h2>
              <p><img src="./images/s_e_planter_250_188.jpg" class="left-image"/>If you have an outdoor space that needs some love -- be it a yard, balcony, rooftop, or an overgrown briar patch draped in popped birthday balloons and broken dreams -- we want to help you transform it into something more beautiful and productive.</p>
